{
  "stem": "14737.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some boy, for some reason, didn't know the answer, he would whisper him the answer, not to make him ashamed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was the type of man who was so honest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Coming back, so I finished fourth grade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father and my mother-- my mother was still alive at that time-- somehow saw that it's a small town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you cannot go so far.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They wanted their children should become something, should have much more education than you can have here in Dolha, a small, little town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after finishing fourth grade, they did send me to a town, Beregsaz, not far from Dolha.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is about approximately three hours [INAUDIBLE] to train, to study to go there to the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Beregsaz, there were two gymnasiums-- a Hungarian gymnasium and a Russian gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Hungarian gymnasium was mostly Hungarian and Jewish also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because this was a town, 95% Hungarians, talking Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's where I learned Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But since basically I didn't know Hungarian, I couldn't start to go to school there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my father send me to that school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was during the Czechoslovakian regime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a school gymnasium of eight years, eighth, eighth grade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's, in comparison like here, like, I would say, a high school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we learned a lot of languages and mathematics, whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, who were the teachers here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the Carpathian, very few intellectuals went for a career of being a teacher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even there were teachers maybe in the elementary school in little town, there was, there was a teacher school in [INAUDIBLE], but after World War I, very few teacher schools.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
